fidelcor ficr unit acquires lazere financial fidelcor inc s fidelcor business credit corp subsidiary said it reached a definitive agreement to acquire a substantial portion of the bank of new england corp s bkne lazere financial corp s assets terms of the acquisition were not disclosed the acquisition is subject to approval of the federal reserve board fidelcor said it would acquire most of lazere s loan portfolio and other assets including its miami office it said it plans to hire the majority of lazere s employees reuter 